With the Oscar’s last night and the Junos tonight I was all in my feels!

First off the Oscars were so amazing and inspiring with so much Asian representation 🙌🏻❤️😭

This picture is from the red carpet of the Juno awards the year I was nominated (2005) for R&B recording of the year - I was told at the time I was the first solo Asian female to be EVER nominated in the category! Like what???? And F!ck yeah!! I have always enjoyed breaking down walls. 🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻

To see someone like you on television it does something magical to your self worth. It says “Hey you!! That thing everyone said you couldn’t do is being done right in front of your eyes - You can do anything!!!!” 

Long story short - I am inspired and I pray that I can inspire in return ⭐️🏆🔆

Life is better with u @thenameisish

You would never say that to your best friend or partner so why do you say it to yourself???

We are all a work in progress and self talk is everything!! It is so important to love yourself. Thoughts become things so next time you find yourself in a negative fear spiral about yourself say these next affirmations! Say them all or just say the ones that resonate with you. ❤️❤️❤️

I AM affirmations
1. I am worthy.
2. I am successful.
3. I am wealthy.
4. I am happy.
5. I am blessed.
6. I am a blessing.
7. I am beautiful, inside and out.
8. I am strong.
9. I am patient.
10. I am resilient.
11. I am rich.
12. I am loved.
13. I am grateful.
14. I am compassionate.
15. I am making a difference in this world.
16. I am a force to be reckoned with.
17. I am capable.
18. I am aware of my strengths.
19. I am peaceful.
20. I am breathing in relaxation.
21. I am deeply motivated to work towards my goals.
22. I am achieving more and more success.
23. I am taking time for self-care.
24. I am grateful that I understand what matters to me.
25. I am reliable.
26. I am loyal.
27. I am immensely creative.
28. I am a go-getter.
29. I am always the first to appreciate other people.
30. I am kind and caring.
Happy Thursday friends! Never take yourself too seriously - When in doubt ugly dance it out ❤️👯‍♀️
